Package: iBiogeobears
Type: Package
Title: Reproducible BioGeoBEARS Workflows, Synthesis, Visualization, and Reporting
Version: 0.1.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Wei", "Xu", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "your.email@example.com")
Author: Wei Xu [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Wei Xu <your.email@example.com>
Description: Provides a reproducible workflow layer around BioGeoBEARS for
    single-clade historical biogeography analyses. The package reads a simple
    YAML configuration file, validates inputs, prepares project output
    directories, checks for an external BioGeoBEARS installation, saves raw
    analysis artifacts, summarizes model comparisons with methodological
    cautions, and prepares publication-oriented tables, figures, and Quarto
    reports. BioGeoBEARS is not bundled and must be installed separately by
    users.
